<figureCitation box="[328,362,585,611]" captionStart="FIGURES 4" captionStartId="13.[151,275,1787,1814]" captionTargetBox="[166,1426,191,1748]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[151,1436,181,1763]" captionText="FIGURES 4A–H. Female pregenital sternites and valvulae of species of Daimachus: A–D, sternites VI and VII of (A) D. exemplificatus Distant, (B) D. matheranensis sp. nov., (C) D. robustus sp. nov. and (D) D. sudindicus sp. nov.; E–H, D. exemplificatus (EF) valvulae I and (GH) valvulae II." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3406227/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">4B</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[374,387,584,611]" captionStart="FIGURES 5" captionStartId="14.[151,275,1889,1916]" captionTargetBox="[156,1426,184,1853]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[151,1436,179,1864]" captionText="FIGURES 5A–L. Valvulae I and II of species of Daimachus: A–D, D. matheranensis sp. nov.; E–H, D. robustus sp. nov. I–L, D. sudindicus sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3406229/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">5</figureCitation>
A–D.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,657,1187]" box="[151,538,657,683]" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">Brown with dark brown markings.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,657,1187]" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">Crown short, about 4.4x as broad as long medially, not much produced in front of eyes.; frontoclypeus strongly convex in profile. Forewings not narrowed posteriorly, of similar width and broadly rounded posteriorly, 2.3x as long as wide. Hind wings present and pronotum convex in lateral view.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,657,1187]" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">
<emphasis box="[199,389,801,827]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">Female genitalia</emphasis>
. Sternite VII with posterior margin broadly angularly excavated (
<figureCitation box="[1116,1203,801,827]" captionStart="FIGURES 4" captionStartId="13.[151,275,1787,1814]" captionTargetBox="[166,1426,191,1748]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[151,1436,181,1763]" captionText="FIGURES 4A–H. Female pregenital sternites and valvulae of species of Daimachus: A–D, sternites VI and VII of (A) D. exemplificatus Distant, (B) D. matheranensis sp. nov., (C) D. robustus sp. nov. and (D) D. sudindicus sp. nov.; E–H, D. exemplificatus (EF) valvulae I and (GH) valvulae II." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3406227/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">Fig. 4B</figureCitation>
). Valvula II with less acutely formed teeth with secondary dentition (
<figureCitation box="[681,770,836,863]" captionStart="FIGURES 5" captionStartId="14.[151,275,1889,1916]" captionTargetBox="[156,1426,184,1853]" captionTargetId="figure@14.[151,1436,179,1864]" captionText="FIGURES 5A–L. Valvulae I and II of species of Daimachus: A–D, D. matheranensis sp. nov.; E–H, D. robustus sp. nov. I–L, D. sudindicus sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3406229/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">Fig. 5D</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,657,1187]" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">
<emphasis box="[199,361,874,899]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="561">Measurements</emphasis>
. Female 
<quantity box="[467,554,873,899]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.2" pageId="4" pageNumber="561" unit="mm" value="4.2">4.2 mm</quantity>
long, 
<quantity box="[627,714,873,899]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.6" pageId="4" pageNumber="561" unit="mm" value="1.6">1.6 mm</quantity>
wide across eyes and 
<quantity box="[969,1056,872,899]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="4" pageNumber="561" unit="mm" value="1.5">1.5 mm</quantity>
wide across posterolateral angels of pronotum.
</paragraph>
